story :
There's a giant who's gone mad. Crazy for food. Everything is eaten. That's the name of the red giant.

The lyrics of the song are often sung by small children when they see the arrival of the Duo Saka red to save their village from enemy attacks, some said that this kind giant appears and disappears by riding the wind.
